09/02/2008: XHarness 1.0-SNAPSHOT (To be included in 1.0-beta3)

    New features:


    Bug fixes:
    * XHARNESS-5: XhExecTaskTest failing on Mac OSX.


08/08/2008: XHarness 1.0-beta2

    New features:
    * Add attribute to output matching to ignore ANSI markups. Default behaviour is ignoreansi=false, when true output matching will ignore ANSI markups to text.

    Bug fixes:
    * Fixed KillTask failing despite failonerror=false when process task is not registered
    * Fixed unix launcher to ignore exit codes corresponding to signals 2(130), 15(143) and a strange exit code 208
    * Fixed ConcurrentModificationException in LineBuffer
